message: Hi Bob, I'm looking to sell this product and believe it would be valuable to you. I'm asking for $15,000 for it. What do you think?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I am only able to pay up to $10,000 for the product. Thank you for understanding.
Thanks for the offer, Bob. I'm willing to come down a bit, but $10,000 is too low for me.  How about $13,000?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your willingness to negotiate. I am still unable to pay more than $10,000 for the product. Thank you for considering my offer.
